OL,3,CPeople advised not to drink tap water
OL,4,Cdue to treatment damage
OL,6,FPeople in parts of the Scottish
OL,7,FBorders are being advised not to drink
OL,8,Ftap water after damage was found in
OL,9,Fits treatment works.
OL,11,FScottish Water identified a fault at
OL,12,FRawburn Water Treatment Works in
OL,13,FBurnmouth, resulting in the water
OL,14,Fquality falling below its "normally
OL,15,Fhigh standard".
OL,17,FAlmost 275 properties have been left
OL,18,Fwithout water while emergency repairs
OL,19,Fare carried out. Bottled water is
OL,20,Fbeing sent to homes across Duns,
OL,21,FLongformacus and Preston.
