OL,6,FEast Berwickshire Independent Cllr
OL,7,FJames Anderson says the region is
OL,8,Ffacing a "serious situation".
OL,10,FHe said: "It is all hands on deck at
OL,11,FScottish Water, and the last report
OL,12,Fwas that they are asking for
OL,13,Fvolunteers around the Chirnside area
OL,14,Fto deliver water to people.
OL,16,F"Water has been cut off across
OL,17,FChirnside and other villages as they
OL,18,Fwork on the problem.
