OL,3,CPeople advised not to drink tap water
OL,4,Cdue to treatment damage
OL,6,F"Obviously this is a very concerning
OL,7,Fsituation, however, Scottish Water are
OL,8,Fworking on the problem, and we hope
OL,9,Ffor an update soon."
OL,11,FIn a notice to customers today, a
OL,12,FScottish Water spokesperson said: "In
OL,13,Fthe early afternoon of Tuesday 26th
OL,14,FAugust, our teams isolated a storage
OL,15,Ftank and Rawburn Water Treatment Works
OL,16,F(WTW) whilst we undertook
OL,17,Finvestigations.
