OL,3,CPeople advised not to drink tap water
OL,4,Cdue to treatment damage
OL,6,F"Our investigations at Rawburn Water
OL,7,FTreatment Works identified a damaged
OL,8,Fsection of water main impacting our
OL,9,Ftreatment processes.
OL,11,F"Our teams worked through the night to
OL,12,Finstall overland supply pipes here to
OL,13,Fbypass this section of damaged water
OL,14,Fmain, along with cleaning of our water
OL,15,Ftanks, and are now in the process of
OL,16,Frestarting our treatment works and
OL,17,Fprocesses to restore water supplies.
