OL,3,CPeople advised not to drink tap water
OL,4,Cdue to treatment damage
OL,6,F"Throughout yesterday evening our
OL,7,Fteams went door to door of the 275
OL,8,Fproperties affected, providing bottled
OL,9,Fwater and precautionary notification
OL,10,FDO NOT use letters and leaflets for
OL,11,Fdrinking or cooking."
OL,13,FAll customers are being asked not to
OL,14,Fuse tap water for drinking, cleaning
OL,15,Fteeth, preparing baby feeds,
OL,16,Fdisinfecting equipment, food
OL,17,Fpreparation, pet food and drink, or
OL,18,Fwashing open wounds.
